description: The part conversion and alteration of existing buildings and the erection of new buildings ranging in height between 2 and 7 storeys to provide: 453 residential units, 3557 m2 B1 floorspace: 505 m2 D1 floorspace (GP surgery or similar): 155 m2 A3 floorspace (cafe or similar): 102 m2 A1 floorspace (local retail shop or similar): 75 m2 D2 floorspace (community meeting room): up to 280 car parking spaces (including off-site provision of 103 spaces).
